{"tid":1604691,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"十月一日大家千祈唔好搞馬場！！！","createTime":"2019-09-30T04:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T07:40:25.000Z","uid":120458,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e18d394ab72eca18c79948a37cd49a7556722ac4","tid":1604691,"uid":120458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"跑少一次馬少十幾億<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬會年年捐七成盈利做慈善，你諗到既公共設施好多都係馬會起，近既有故宮博物館，舊啲既有科大，甚至海洋公園都係馬會起。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬會啲高層好謹慎架，你地一吹風話燒馬場，佢地就會落柯打唔跑馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔取消賽事，popo放tg，咁啲馬死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你估馬會最緊張啲乜？就係佢啲馬呀！<br />\n<br />\n所以求求大家千祈唔好搞馬場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c291e4f5a1ee786dcb1554da5480c3126b9b9385","tid":1604691,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:06:32.000Z","msg":"跑馬地嗰邊有巴站出南區做避難所"},{"pid":"f63edfe053272fdfeaa8eee037eaf3c1973234d5","tid":1604691,"uid":120458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c291e4f5a1ee786dcb1554da5480c3126b9b9385","tid":1604691,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:06:32.000Z","msg":"跑馬地嗰邊有巴站出南區做避難所"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:07:40.000Z","msg":"國慶杯喺沙田搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967440b7c19ec100e32e8be4e5297af13c44ac5d","tid":1604691,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f63